        </p>

        <p><iframe style="margin-top:20px" width="100%" height="500px" frameBorder="0" src="https://umap.openstreetmap.fr/en/map/nuit-debout-paris-plan-de-la-republique_80910?scaleControl=false&miniMap=false&scrollWheelZoom=false&zoomControl=true&allowEdit=false&moreControl=true&datalayersControl=true&onLoadPanel=databrowser&captionBar=false"></iframe><p><a href="https://umap.openstreetmap.fr/en/map/nuit-debout-paris-plan-de-la-republique_80910">See full screen</a></p>

